name: language_html_data_attribute_unquoted_tag_breakout
description: |
  In an unquoted attribute this value closes the current tag and introduces an
  inert custom element. It is a non-executing canary for templates that omit
  quotes or rely on validation instead of output encoding.
format: utf8-strip
decode-as: ascii
tags:
  - "language"
  - "html"
  - "xss"
  - "xss-data"
  - "html-attribute-context"
  - "unquoted-attribute"
  - "greater-than"
  - "dom-injection"
  - "inert-canary"
---
x><x-xss-canary>
